<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad"
>

  <body>
    <div metal:fill-slot="main">
      <p>We are planning to relicense all translations submitted
        through Launchpad under BSD license.  This will clarify
        licensing used for translations in Launchpad:
        for further explanations, please see
        <a href="http://help.launchpad.net/Translations/RelicensingFAQ">
        Relicensing FAQ</a>.</p>

      <p>You can choose not to relicense your translations,
        and they will be <strong>removed</strong> when we migrate to
        BSD licensed translations completely.  You will be able to change
        your opinion at least until end of June, through your
        <a tal:attributes="href string:${context/fmt:url}/+relicensing">
         relicensing translations</a> page.</p>

      <div metal:use-macro="context/@@launchpad_form/form" />
    </div>
  </body>

</html>
